// HTMX vendor file is downloaded at Docker build time (or fetched manually
// for local dev). To keep the repo lean, we don't commit the minified
// blob. To install for local dev:
//
//   curl -L -o static/htmx.min.js https://unpkg.com/htmx.org@2.0.4/dist/htmx.min.js
//
// In Dockerfile, add the same curl step. Until then, the viewer page will
// fall back to no-HTMX (slider still moves, but partial updates won't
// fire -- viewer.js does the URL update via history.replaceState even
// without HTMX so deep links keep working).
